# TC32 : ObstacleDetected9
# Precondition : NormalMode, forward=false
# Action : left + right obstacle detected, front clear
# Expected : no change from backward escape state, forward=false remains
power
start
expect mode NormalMode
obstacle 1 1 1
expect motorForward false
obstacle 0 1 1
expect mode NormalMode
expect cleaner on
expect motor moving
expect motorForward false
exit
